{"id":6041,"date":"2015-04-04T07:00:57","date_gmt":"2015-04-04T13:00:57","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/?p=6041"},"modified":"2018-12-08T11:41:14","modified_gmt":"2018-12-08T18:41:14","slug":"miniature-succulent-bird-cages","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/miniature-succulent-bird-cages\/","title":{"rendered":"Miniature Succulent Bird Cages"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-0 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\"><p><em>You're likely aware that succulents are cute in anything, but these miniature succulent bird cages are to die for! Find out how to make your own!<\/em><\/p>\n<p>I always love finding new containers to plant succulents in. I filled a large birdcage with succulents a while ago (I can't reveal it until December because it was part of a large project I'm working on). While it was fun, it was also a lot of work. While I was out shopping I came across these miniature birdcages and thought they would make a quick and fun succulent project so I got three!<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6047 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Im-dying-over-these-gorgeous-little-succulent-filled-bird-cages-So-cute.jpg\" alt=\"I'm dying over these gorgeous little succulent filled bird cages! So cute!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Im-dying-over-these-gorgeous-little-succulent-filled-bird-cages-So-cute-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Im-dying-over-these-gorgeous-little-succulent-filled-bird-cages-So-cute-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Im-dying-over-these-gorgeous-little-succulent-filled-bird-cages-So-cute.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>If you want to make your own miniature birdcages, here is what you'll need:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Succulents (I used <a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_golden&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F181169020%2Fsucculent-plant-sedum-nussbaumerianum-or%3Fga_order%3Dmost_relevant%26ga_search_type%3Dall%26ga_view_type%3Dgallery%26ga_search_query%3Dgolden%2520sedum%26ref%3Dsr_gallery_16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Golden Sedum<\/a>,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_donkey&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F208534573%2Fdonkey-tail-cluster-sedum-morganianum%3Fref%3Dshop_home_active_13%26ga_search_query%3Dsedum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Donkey's Tail<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_calico&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F172649756%2Fsucculent-plant-crassula-calico-kitten%3Fga_order%3Dmost_relevant%26ga_search_type%3Dall%26ga_view_type%3Dgallery%26ga_search_query%3Dcalico%2520kitten%2520succulent%26ref%3Dsr_gallery_4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Calico Kitten<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_sunset&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F181054408%2Fsucculent-plant-california-sunset-this%3Fga_order%3Dmost_relevant%26ga_search_type%3Dall%26ga_view_type%3Dgallery%26ga_search_query%3Dcalifornia%2520sunset%2520succulent%26ref%3Dsr_gallery_21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">California Sunset<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_thimble&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F197462739%2Fthimble-cactus-cluster-mammillaria%3Fga_order%3Dmost_relevant%26ga_search_type%3Dall%26ga_view_type%3Dgallery%26ga_search_query%3Dthimble%2520cactus%26ref%3Dsr_gallery_4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Thimble Cactus<\/a>)<\/li>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Miniature Bird Cages (see below)<\/li>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B000UGPWES\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=390957&creativeASIN=B000UGPWES&linkCode=as2&tag=cassituttlpho-20&linkId=JBNU7YKFIBJNUBRR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Sphagnum moss<\/a><\/li>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Optional: <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/1AOWsGn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Floral glue<\/a><\/li>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Optional: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bonsaijack.com\/Succulent_Soil_sas.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Succulent soil<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>I found my bird cages at Michael's, but if you'd like to order online I\u00a0found a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_birdcages&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F213989814%2Fset-of-2-antique-bronze-metal-bird-cage%3Fga_order%3Dmost_relevant%26ga_search_type%3Dall%26ga_view_type%3Dgallery%26ga_search_query%3Dmetal%2520bird%2520cage%26ref%3Dsr_gallery_5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">set of two on Etsy<\/a> that is similar. There are also these <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=blog&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dtiny%2520bird%2520cage%2520\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">itty bitty bird cages<\/a> that would be cute too! I haven't ordered from either of these shops but they get good reviews. Hobby Lobby also carries some small bird cages. If you're looking to make these for wedding decorations, Amazon <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/1FvzGyU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">has a set of 12<\/a>\u00a0that is really cute.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6044 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Find-out-how-to-plant-succulents-in-mini-birdcages-like-this-one.jpg\" alt=\"Find out how to plant succulents in mini birdcages like this one\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Find-out-how-to-plant-succulents-in-mini-birdcages-like-this-one-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Find-out-how-to-plant-succulents-in-mini-birdcages-like-this-one-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Find-out-how-to-plant-succulents-in-mini-birdcages-like-this-one.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Look for something that opens up from the top so it's easy to put succulents in. It was also nice that the bars were far enough apart I could have the Calico Kitten succulent hang over the edge of the bird cage.<\/p>\n<h3>Instructions<\/h3>\n<p>Start by soaking your sphagnum moss with water. Take a small handful and place it on the bottom of the birdcage. If you want to make sure it stays put, use some floral glue to adhere it to the birdcage. If your birdcage is fairly deep, you may want to create a deeper pile of moss and add your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bonsaijack.com\/Succulent_Soil_sas.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">succulent soil<\/a> to it. This will help the succulents last much longer without needing to be replanted.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6052 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Use-sphagnum-moss-as-a-potting-medium-for-succulents-in-a-birdcage.jpg\" alt=\"Use sphagnum moss as a potting medium for succulents in a birdcage\" width=\"735\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Use-sphagnum-moss-as-a-potting-medium-for-succulents-in-a-birdcage-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Use-sphagnum-moss-as-a-potting-medium-for-succulents-in-a-birdcage-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Use-sphagnum-moss-as-a-potting-medium-for-succulents-in-a-birdcage.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Once the moss is in place, add your succulents!<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6042 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Add-succulents-to-a-miniature-birdcage-for-a-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Add succulents to a miniature birdcage for a decoration\" width=\"735\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Add-succulents-to-a-miniature-birdcage-for-a-decoration-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Add-succulents-to-a-miniature-birdcage-for-a-decoration-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Add-succulents-to-a-miniature-birdcage-for-a-decoration.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>I decided to add one more succulent to fill the bird cage more. Close the lid once you have them all arranged and you're done!<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6043 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Fill-a-bird-cage-with-succulents-for-a-fun-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Fill a bird cage with succulents for a fun decoration\" width=\"735\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Fill-a-bird-cage-with-succulents-for-a-fun-decoration-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Fill-a-bird-cage-with-succulents-for-a-fun-decoration-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/Fill-a-bird-cage-with-succulents-for-a-fun-decoration.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Here are the three that I created.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6051 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/This-little-succulent-filled-bird-cage-is-so-cute.jpg\" alt=\"This little succulent filled bird cage is so cute!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/This-little-succulent-filled-bird-cage-is-so-cute-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/This-little-succulent-filled-bird-cage-is-so-cute-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/This-little-succulent-filled-bird-cage-is-so-cute.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6045 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/I-love-how-these-succulents-look-in-this-miniature-bird-cage.jpg\" alt=\"I love how these succulents look in this miniature bird cage!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/I-love-how-these-succulents-look-in-this-miniature-bird-cage-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/I-love-how-these-succulents-look-in-this-miniature-bird-cage-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/I-love-how-these-succulents-look-in-this-miniature-bird-cage.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6049 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-succulents-look-adorable-in-this-little-birdcage.jpg\" alt=\"These succulents look adorable in this little birdcage!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-succulents-look-adorable-in-this-little-birdcage-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-succulents-look-adorable-in-this-little-birdcage-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-succulents-look-adorable-in-this-little-birdcage.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>While I love how they look individually, the grouping is so much more fun! You can hang these out in the garden or use them as a centerpiece for a table. I used <a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=birdcages_twine&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F115187151%2Fjute-twine-3ply-28lb-natural-jute-100%3Fga_order%3Dmost_relevant%26ga_search_type%3Dall%26ga_view_type%3Dgallery%26ga_search_query%3Djute%2520twine%26ref%3Dsr_gallery_9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">twine<\/a> to hang these in my Aunt's garden. She has a gorgeous space full of plants and also loves birds and birdcages so I thought these would be\u00a0a nice gift for her.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6053 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/What-a-fun-decoration-Succulents-in-little-bird-cages.jpg\" alt=\"What a fun decoration! Succulents in little bird cages\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/What-a-fun-decoration-Succulents-in-little-bird-cages-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/What-a-fun-decoration-Succulents-in-little-bird-cages-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/What-a-fun-decoration-Succulents-in-little-bird-cages.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6050 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-suculents-in-little-bird-cages-are-adorable.jpg\" alt=\"These succulents in little bird cages are adorable!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-suculents-in-little-bird-cages-are-adorable-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-suculents-in-little-bird-cages-are-adorable-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/06\/These-suculents-in-little-bird-cages-are-adorable.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>I'm really happy with how these little guys turned out and they were super easy to make! So, if you're looking for a quick project that looks amazing, give these a try! Also, I'd love to know what you think. Feel free to leave a comment below or send me an email. Shares on Pinterest are always great too \ud83d\ude09<\/p>\n<\/div><div